products.title: Intel Core i3-8350K Desktop Processor 4 Cores up to 4.0 GHz unlocked LGA 1151 300 Series 91W
features: Compatible only with Motherboards based on Intel 300 Series Chipsets
products.description: Prepare to be amazed with the 8th Generation Intel Core Desktop Processor family. The 8th Generation Intel Core i3-8350K comes with 4 processing Cores and 4 Threads. That's 2 additional Cores versus the previous generation for more processing power. With this unlocked processor you have the opportunity to tweak the platform performance for an even better PC experience. Immerse yourself in your favorite media content while the Intel UHD Graphics 630 provides you with a much richer visual experience. Be sure to pair your 8th Gen desktop processor with a motherboard based on the Intel 300 series chipset. Experience new system acceleration when paired with Intel Optane Memory and a 2.5" HDD. Supports two-channel DDR4-2400 memory technology, which allows systems to have up to 64 GB of memory and up to 2400 MT/s memory transfer speeds.
